.7<br>(3.6)\n| style=\"background: #5064FF;\" | 88.2<br>(3.5)\n| style=\"background: #3C50FF;\" | 87.2<br>(3.4)\n| style=\"background:#788cff; border-left:2px solid #bbb;\"| '''854.8'''<br>('''33.7''')\n|- style=\"text-align:center;\"\n! style=\"background:#dcf0f0; color:navy;\"| Rainfall \u2265 1&nbsp;mm<br>days\n| style=\"background: #788CFF;\" | 13.2\n| style=\"background: #A0B4FF;\" | 10.4\n| style=\"background: #8CA0FF;\" | 11.5\n| style=\"background: #A0B4FF;\" | 10.4\n| style=\"background: #A0B4FF;\" | 9.9\n| style=\"background: #A0B4FF;\" | 9.6\n| style=\"background: #A0B4FF;\" | 9.5\n| style=\"background: #A0B4FF;\" | 9.9\n| style=\"background: #A0B4FF;\" | 9.9\n| style=\"background: #788CFF;\" | 12.6\n| style=\"background: #788CFF;\" | 13.1\n| style=\"background: #788CFF;\" | 12.7\n| style=\"background:#8ca0ff; border-left:2px solid #bbb;\"| '''132.8'''\n|-\n| colspan=\"15\" style=\"background:#dcf0f0; color:navy; text-align:center;\"| <small>Source: Met Office<ref name=\"England\">{{cite web | year = 2012 | url = http://www.metoffice.gov.uk/climate/uk/averages/19812010/areal/england.html | title = England averages | publisher = Met Office | accessdate = 6 December 2012 | url-status = dead | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130410093339/http://www.metoffice.gov.uk/climate/uk/averages/19812010/areal/england.html | archivedate = 10 April 2013 | df = dmy-all }}</ref> (1981&ndash;2010 averages) </small>\n|}\n{{clear}}\n\n{{Weather box\n|location = England\n|metric first = y\n|single line = yes\n|Jan record high C = 17.6\n|Feb record high C = 21.2\n|Mar record high C = 25.6\n|Apr record high C = 29.4\n|May record high C = 32.8\n|Jun record high C = 35.6\n|Jul record high C = 38.7\n|Aug record high C = 38.5\n|Sep record high C = 35.6\n|Oct record high C = 29.9\n|Nov record high C = 21.1\n|Dec record high C = 17.7\n|year record high C = \n|Jan record low C = -26.1\n|Feb record low C = -20.6\n|Mar record low C = -21.1\n|Apr record low C = -15.0\n|May rec